item.p:
Where profit on debt does not exceed PKR 5,000,000:
                  15% for persons on the ATL;
                  30% for persons not on the ATL.

Where profit on debt exceeds PKR 5,000,000:
                  17.5% for persons on the ATL;
                  35% for persons not on the ATL.

Services rendered by other persons (individuals, AOPs):
                    10% (ATL);
                    20% (non-ATL).

Supply of goods by other persons (individuals, AOPs):
                    4.5% (ATL);
                    9% (non-ATL).

Annual rent exceeding PKR 2,000,000:
                  15% of the gross amount of rent for ATL persons;
                  30% for non-ATL.

content.p:
The exemption under this section applies to all income derived
              from the business operations of the zone enterprise within the special economic zone,
              including income from manufacturing, processing, assembling, and related activities.
